    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1975-07-28T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1975-07-28T00:00:00-05:00" n="122"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d122">
                <head>122. Memorandum From the Executive Secretary of the 40 Committee (<persName
                        corresp="#p_RRR_1" type="from">Ratliff</persName>) to Director of Central
                    Intelligence <persName corresp="#p_CWE_1" type="to">Colby</persName>
                    <note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d122fn1">Source: National Security Council,
                            <persName corresp="#p_FGR_1">Ford</persName> Administration Intelligence
                        Files, 40 Committee Meetings. Secret; Sensitive; Eyes Only.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            when="1975-07-28">July 28, 1975</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <list type="subject">
                    <head>SUBJECT</head>
                    <item>Angola</item>
                </list>
                <p>On 27 July 1975 higher authority approved the full [<hi rend="italic">dollar
                        amount not declassified</hi>] program incorporated in the <gloss
                        target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss> task group paper “Plan for Covert
                    Action—Angola” which was submitted 16 July 1975.<note n="2" xml:id="d122fn2">
                        <ref target="#d116">Document 116</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <p>This includes the previous approval noted in the minute of 21 July 1975,<note
                        n="3" xml:id="d122fn3">See <ref target="#d118fn2">footnote 2, Document
                            118</ref>.</note> adding [<hi rend="italic">dollar amount not
                        declassified</hi>] of Phase II of the plan for a total approval of [<hi
                        rend="italic">dollar amount not declassified</hi>]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_RRR_1">
                            <hi rend="strong">Rob Roy Ratliff</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
